Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,==========STORY==========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.75,0:00:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然把我們四個都擋住了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.21,0:00:20.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這樣把他們的Mir同化！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.31,0:00:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了 D島的死神
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.64,0:00:31.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥的仇人…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.92,0:00:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艦隊 距離20單位
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.36,0:00:35.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經幾乎到達引擎重啟後可逃脫的極限距離
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.59,0:00:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不啟動就逃不掉了！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,引擎不動 放出飛鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.76,0:00:55.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,通告人類軍士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:00:57.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們正在執行一個作戰行動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.75,0:01:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了將新到來的Mir變為對人類有益的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.78,0:01:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們想將作為我方成果的全部數據提供給各位
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.82,0:01:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.07,0:01:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻過去！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.56,0:01:13.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艦隊展開 我們要被包圍了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.51,0:01:17.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是選擇了對話的人在表明態度
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.33,0:01:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,選擇了對話的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.72,0:01:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到大量通信
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.56,0:01:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是太平洋艦隊 這些難以置信的龐大數據是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.04,0:01:27.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是玻里尼西亞艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.48,0:01:29.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}告訴我們 那裡有Festum嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.18,0:01:28.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壁…是那個真壁嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.52,0:01:32.53,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(500,500)\fs26\pos(953,610)}最終回
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.52,0:01:32.53,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(500,500)\pos(1110,610)}龍宮島
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.18,0:01:31.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都被騙了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.09,0:01:32.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來你們不是敵人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.37,0:01:35.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聲音…傳遞到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.21,0:01:38.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道會變成這樣是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.53,0:01:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們捨棄了新聯合國這個大義名分
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.67,0:01:45.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有足夠的時間統治全軍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵方內核操縱人的手法有限
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.24,0:01:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,發佈交戰規定α
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.49,0:01:53.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肅清反抗分子！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.42,0:01:59.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,操縱被劫持了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.78,0:02:02.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡的真壁！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.11,0:02:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與敵人共存…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.44,0:02:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是被三面計劃所埋葬的道路嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.90,0:02:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全機 更換常規彈藥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.22,0:02:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更改目標
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.25,0:02:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類軍…在幫我們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.06,0:02:33.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,匹配它的波長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.16,0:02:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們來打破它
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.90,0:02:36.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼…媽媽？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.07,0:02:49.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要把希望還回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.95,0:02:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是因為弟弟向Mir許願了才能活下來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:57.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像你許願讓弓子活下來一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.46,0:03:01.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.08,0:03:03.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.26,0:03:05.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽還好好的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要！我不要媽媽不見！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.66,0:03:11.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 媽媽……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.76,0:03:16.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光弘！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.27,0:03:20.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.49,0:03:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真壁…由我來…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.87,0:03:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,FENRIR, start
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.87,0:03:26.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,655)}芬里爾啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.50,0:03:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是人…可是我能感受到她的心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:31.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別猶豫 一騎！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.39,0:03:35.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來幫你消除你和Mir的調和
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:43.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}5 4 3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.04,0:03:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫我們…實現希望…光弘…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.87,0:03:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,FENRIR, execute
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.87,0:03:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(640,655)}芬里爾 引爆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.39,0:03:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一騎!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:50.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.85,0:04:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把你們全殺了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:06.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.65,0:04:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高帕一閃！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.68,0:04:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.64,0:05:01.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿育？怎麼復活的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用迴轉體破壞你的護壁！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.11,0:05:18.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再生速度太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.62,0:05:21.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是那部機體的能力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:26.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 變成我的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.67,0:05:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,島的Mir在保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:38.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拒絕他 一騎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.50,0:05:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總士！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.54,0:05:54.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到天上去！在地上會把島打沉的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.75,0:06:11.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽 不要走…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.49,0:06:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我總算能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.33,0:06:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的能力有多麼了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.62,0:06:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要相信自己
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.88,0:06:23.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論在任何時候
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.64,0:06:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽……
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:31.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和爸爸都在你的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.98,0:06:35.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.89,0:06:53.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:01.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽……
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.66,0:07:04.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能遇到你真好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.84,0:07:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我最好的朋友 美羽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.60,0:07:12.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你別走 艾梅莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.10,0:07:17.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的生命會和這個島的Mir一起不斷循環
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.38,0:07:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以後再說很多很多的話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.57,0:07:26.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾梅莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:41.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是一段漫長的路途
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我把這條生命還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.33,0:07:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充滿世界吧 我們的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.18,0:08:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死神 給我消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:05.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,FENRIR, start
